column4: i'm having some trouble here.. rhythmbox won't import my mp3's, and xmms won't play them (crashes).. i have installed tons of mp3-related libs and codecs and stuff, none did it.. and btw system sounds play just fine, it's not that..
xmms problem: change the output plugin to esound
eclipse-nls-sdk - localized message catalog for eclipse  - that's it
